                            <comment id="13060191" author="stack" created="Tue, 5 Jul 2011 23:22:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Andrew.  I think 451 in 90 too big a change (it&apos;s not finished yet on trunk).  Meantime the fix by the lads from huawei should do in the meantime.  We just need to push out 0.90.4&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
